modName: Demi Rose Bodyslide Preset UUNP HDT
summary: This mod tries to replicate the body of Demi Rose, this is a UUNP Bodyslide.
descriptionHtml:
!!!IMPORTANT THIS PRESET IS SUPPOSED TO BE USED WITH 100 WEIGHT!!!

Credits to : AllHailPlankton : For providing me with the last 2 screenshots!!

This is a preset I wanted many people to make for me, I asked many modders to help me but all of them stopped taking requests so I tried to make a brief copy of the body by myself. Please feel free to send me some screenshots.


Installation: 

Drop the .xml file to Data\CalienteTools\BodySlide\SliderPresets

and go to your bodyslide application and create body for both armors and nude.
